Torfinn is a sailor located in north Rellekka on a dock. He assists the player during Dragon Slayer II. He uses his boat to sail to the island of Ungael where the dragon Vorkath resides.

Should the player die in battle to Vorkath, players can retrieve their items from him for a fee of 100,000 coins. This fee can be taken directly from the player's bank.
